but I'm not going to lead you on.

1101
01:38:54.346 --> 01:38:55.972 line:82%
You're a really nice guy, Rohan,

1102
01:38:57.182 --> 01:39:00.560 line:82%
and I know that you would make
any girl really happy,

1103
01:39:01.102 --> 01:39:02.646 line:82%
but I'm not ready yet.

1104
01:39:03.521 --> 01:39:05.732 line:82%
I'm not ready for marriage.

1105
01:39:05.815 --> 01:39:08.151 line:82%
Who said I was ready?

1106
01:39:11.071 --> 01:39:14.491 line:82%
What do you think? I go around
chasing girls all over the place?

1107
01:39:16.326 --> 01:39:19.454 line:82%
You know, Pooja,
l don't believe in arranged marriages.

1108
01:39:20.538 --> 01:39:22.666 line:82%
l just happened to see your photo...

1109
01:39:23.625 --> 01:39:28.922 line:82%
and I don't know why,
l felt I had to meet you.

1110
01:39:30.632 --> 01:39:35.261 line:82%
Then I heard that you weren't ready
to meet, so I forgot all about it.

1111
01:39:36.596 --> 01:39:40.100 line:82%
Then all of a sudden, yesterday,
there you were,

1112
01:39:41.601 --> 01:39:44.979 line:82%
and I thought you could use a friend.

1113
01:39:46.439 --> 01:39:50.235 line:82%
That's why I'm here,
just to get to know you better.

1114
01:39:51.611 --> 01:39:56.491 line:82%
No promises, no strings, just friendship.

1115
01:39:57.117 --> 01:39:59.828 line:82%
If nothing else, you'll make a friend.

1116
01:40:01.454 --> 01:40:02.872 line:82%
Will you be my friend?

1117
01:40:04.916 --> 01:40:08.253 line:82%
Try me. My friends say I'm a good friend.

1118
01:40:11.089 --> 01:40:14.676 line:82%
Let me warn you, Pooja,
when girls make friends with me,

1119
01:40:15.260 --> 01:40:18.096 line:82%
the friendship usually changes into love.

1120
01:40:18.304 --> 01:40:21.641 line:82%
-Tea?
-Here or somewhere else?

1121
01:40:21.725 --> 01:40:22.976 line:82%
Rohan.

1122
01:40:29.149 --> 01:40:30.293 line:82%
Raj.

1123
01:40:30.358 --> 01:40:35.238 line:82%
You don't have to tell me, I know.
What are you doing? Thinking about me?

1124
01:40:35.655 --> 01:40:37.282 line:82%
What else do I do in the office?

1125
01:40:37.907 --> 01:40:39.993 line:82%
-Liar.
-That's right, I was working.

1126
01:40:40.326 --> 01:40:44.631 line:82%
-Your lies are better than the truth.
-Okay, don't disturb me. Let me work.

1127
01:40:44.706 --> 01:40:47.834 line:82%
Working? Ten days before our wedding?

1128
01:40:48.543 --> 01:40:52.380 line:82%
Ten days and so much to do.

1129
01:40:52.839 --> 01:40:57.886 line:82%
Enough. Take me out.
I'm bored sitting at home.

1130
01:40:57.970 --> 01:41:01.681 line:82%
We'll go out this evening.
Go shopping with Pooja.

1131
01:41:02.182 --> 01:41:05.351 line:82%
Pooja's out. Why else would I call you?

1132
01:41:05.435 --> 01:41:07.312 line:82%
Gone out? Where?

1133
01:41:07.395 --> 01:41:09.731 line:82%
-To the movies with Rohan.
-With Rohan?

1134
01:41:09.814 --> 01:41:11.691 line:82%
Yes, he's too cool.

1135
01:41:11.775 --> 01:41:15.278 line:82%
l think they have something going.
Wouldn't that be great?

1136
01:41:15.365 --> 01:41:19.199 line:82%
-Yeah. Where'd they go?
-How should I know?

1137
01:41:19.282 --> 01:41:22.911 line:82%
Hey, Mr. America, tell me now,
are you taking me out or not?

1138
01:41:23.870 --> 01:41:27.665 line:82%
Hey, Miss Universe,
I'll be there in ten minutes. Be ready.

1139
01:41:27.999 --> 01:41:30.126 line:82%
-I love you, Raj!
-Bye.

1140
01:41:53.191 --> 01:41:57.278 line:82%
The film starts in three minutes.
l don't want to miss the beginning.

1141
01:41:57.362 --> 01:42:00.031 line:82%
We're next.
You won't miss the beginning.

1142
01:42:00.240 --> 01:42:03.451 line:82%
Even the line for the popcorn is long.

1143
01:42:03.535 --> 01:42:07.330 line:82%
Up to you. The beginning of the movie
or popcorn? Decide.

1144
01:42:08.331 --> 01:42:11.626 line:82%
Okay, go watch the beginning,
I'll get the popcorn.

1145
01:42:11.709 --> 01:42:14.045 line:82%
-Raj, you're so sweet.
-Next, please.

1146
01:42:19.342 --> 01:42:21.970 line:82%
-Two popcorns.
-Hey, make that four.

1147
01:42:22.720 --> 01:42:25.849 line:82%
-Where were you guys?
-Showing Pooja around London.

1148
01:42:25.932 --> 01:42:30.645 line:82%
But she's seen everything already.
so I figured we'd catch a movie.

1149
01:42:30.728 --> 01:42:33.439 line:82%
-Maybe she hasn't seen it already.
-Where's Tina?

1150
01:42:33.523 --> 01:42:37.652 line:82%
-Inside. She wanted to catch the start.
-The movie has started?

1151
01:42:37.735 --> 01:42:43.116 line:82%
Then what are we doing here?
Come on, let's go. Raj, you talk too much.

1152
01:42:43.199 --> 01:42:44.367 line:82%
Thank you.

1153
01:42:49.831 --> 01:42:51.332 line:82%
-Hi, Pooja.
-Hi.

1154
01:42:51.416 --> 01:42:54.252 line:82%
-What are you doing here?
-Playing cricket.

1155
01:42:54.335 --> 01:42:56.880 line:82%
Anyways, never mind.
The movie's started.

1156
01:43:12.437 --> 01:43:16.274 line:82%
Raj, where did you learn to make
such wonderful chicken tikka?

1157
01:43:16.691 --> 01:43:20.445 line:82%
-Rohan, are those scratches on your arm?
-Take a look.

1158
01:43:20.653 --> 01:43:25.199 line:82%
Look, fingernail scratches.

1159
01:43:25.283 --> 01:43:27.285 line:82%
Look what your daughter did to my arm.

1160
01:43:27.327 --> 01:43:28.369 line:82%
What?

1161
01:43:28.453 --> 01:43:31.247 line:82%
That's why I never sit next to Pooja
when I watch a horror movie.

1162
01:43:31.331 --> 01:43:34.500 line:82%
And you don't even want to know
what she's like on an airplane.

1163
01:43:34.584 --> 01:43:40.214 line:82%
When she was a kid, I clipped her nails.
Now she won't listen anymore.

1164
01:43:40.965 --> 01:43:43.635 line:82%
Papa, they're making fun of me.

1165
01:43:43.718 --> 01:43:45.929 line:82%
Look, she just scratched me!

1166
01:43:47.096 --> 01:43:49.057 line:82%
I'm lucky it was only 90 minutes.

1167
01:43:49.140 --> 01:43:52.977 line:82%
Had it been a Hindi film,
I'd have said goodbye to my arm.

1168
01:43:53.061 --> 01:43:55.939 line:82%
Laugh it up.
l hope you're enjoying yourselves.

1169
01:43:56.022 --> 01:43:59.984 line:82%
Darling, are you angry?
It's all just a bit of comedy.

1170
01:44:00.193 --> 01:44:02.487 line:82%
-Tina, this is all your fault.
-Really?

1171
01:44:02.582 --> 01:44:06.656 line:82%
-Now go and pacify my daughter.
-I'll do that.

1172
01:44:06.741 --> 01:44:09.171 line:82%
Yes, only my Raj can pacify her.

1173
01:44:09.744 --> 01:44:12.121 line:82%
Hey, Raj, I'll go.

1174
01:44:13.164 --> 01:44:14.203 line:82%
Sure.

1175
01:44:21.798 --> 01:44:25.393 line:82%
Somebody said that being friends
means never having to say you're sorry.

1176
01:44:25.885 --> 01:44:27.470 line:82%
Still, I've come to apologize.

1177
01:44:30.181 --> 01:44:33.828 line:82%
If you're friends you don't do something
that you have to apologize for.

1178
01:44:34.352 --> 01:44:36.354 line:82%
You're right, but what can I do?

1179
01:44:36.437 --> 01:44:39.524 line:82%
If I'm in the mood for a joke,
I sometimes cross the line.

1180
01:44:41.651 --> 01:44:43.835 line:82%
Did I cross the line this time?

1181
01:44:46.322 --> 01:44:49.659 line:82%
Rohan you're too much.
Nobody can stay angry with you.

1182
01:44:49.909 --> 01:44:52.620 line:82%
That's because I'm so cute and adorable.

1183
01:44:53.371 --> 01:44:57.041 line:82%
Okay, Mr. Cute-and-adorable,
it's late. Good night.

1184
01:44:57.333 --> 01:45:01.713 line:82%
Good night? That means get out.
Okay, I'm going.

1185
01:45:02.880 --> 01:45:04.257 line:82%
-Bye.
-Bye.

1186
01:45:05.800 --> 01:45:07.051 line:82%
-Good night.
-Good night.

1187
01:45:08.469 --> 01:45:11.431 line:82%
-You've calmed down, right?
-Yes, Rohan.

1188
01:45:12.765 --> 01:45:13.891 line:82%
Just checking.

1189
01:45:15.435 --> 01:45:18.187 line:82%
-So we're still friends, right?
-Yes.

1190
01:45:20.106 --> 01:45:23.108 line:82%
-So we'll see each other tomorrow, right?
-Yes, Rohan.

1191
01:45:23.192 --> 01:45:24.235 line:82%
Cool.

1192
01:45:25.903 --> 01:45:28.031 line:82%
-Will you marry me?
-What?

1193
01:45:28.823 --> 01:45:31.743 line:82%
You were saying yes to everything,
so I thought I'd give it a shot.

1194
01:45:31.826 --> 01:45:34.662 line:82%
-Rohan.
-Is that a yes or a no?

1195
01:45:36.581 --> 01:45:38.113 line:82%
That's a no.

1196
01:45:38.207 --> 01:45:40.376 line:82%
-Okay, bye.
-Bye.

1197
01:45:41.711 --> 01:45:42.879 line:82%
Rohan.

1198
01:45:47.008 --> 01:45:48.176 line:82%
Raj.

1199
01:45:58.561 --> 01:45:59.562 line:82%
Raj.

1200
01:46:22.960 --> 01:46:24.003 line:82%
Tina.

1201
01:46:27.131 --> 01:46:28.424 line:82%
Penny for your thoughts.

1202
01:46:28.674 --> 01:46:32.929 line:82%
I'm starting a new chapter of my life,

1203
01:46:34.180 --> 01:46:36.581 line:82%
but it's based on a lie.

1204
01:46:37.225 --> 01:46:39.852 line:82%
Before I start this new life,

1205
01:46:39.936 --> 01:46:44.398 line:82%
l want to tell Raj the truth,
that I didn't write those letters.

1206
01:46:45.566 --> 01:46:50.697 line:82%
Tina, forget about the past.
The important thing is,

1207
01:46:50.780 --> 01:46:54.992 line:82%
you love Raj and you're marrying him.
Nothing else matters.

1208
01:46:55.076 --> 01:46:58.641 line:82%
-But, Pooja--
-No buts. You're the one who says

1209
01:46:58.746 --> 01:47:01.958 line:82%
if you hang on to old memories,
you won't create new ones.

1210
01:47:02.041 --> 01:47:04.418 line:82%
So, come on, forget the past.
Come on. Let's go.

1211
01:47:04.502 --> 01:47:06.462 line:82%
-Pooja.
-Tina.

1212
01:47:10.633 --> 01:47:12.552 line:82%
Hey, Raj. Look at this.

1213
01:47:13.010 --> 01:47:14.988 line:82%
Do you think Pooja will like it?

1214
01:47:16.305 --> 01:47:19.225 line:82%
No, Pooja would never wear that color.

1215
01:47:20.351 --> 01:47:22.269 line:82%
Then which color does she like?

1216
01:47:22.353 --> 01:47:24.814 line:82%
Green, Raj loves green.

1217
01:47:24.897 --> 01:47:28.234 line:82%
Tell me more about what Raj likes.

1218
01:47:28.317 --> 01:47:32.080 line:82%
You used to talk about him all the time,
but not anymore.

1219
01:47:32.155 --> 01:47:35.908 line:82%
She loves the little things,
popcorn, books.

1220
01:47:35.992 --> 01:47:37.118 line:82%
Gobi parathas.

1221
01:47:37.326 --> 01:47:38.744 line:82%
Songs from old Hindi films.

1222
01:47:38.828 --> 01:47:40.446 line:82%
Raj is a very different kind of guy.

1223
01:47:40.637 --> 01:47:42.665 line:82%
Pooja is a completely different sort.

1224
01:47:44.417 --> 01:47:46.318 line:82%
And you never fell in love with Raj?

1225
01:47:47.837 --> 01:47:51.007 line:82%
l did, but you stole him from me.

1226
01:47:55.303 --> 01:47:57.430 line:82%
-Just joking.
-Pooja.

1227
01:47:59.140 --> 01:48:00.975 line:82%
-Here they are.
-Shopping done?

1228
01:48:01.058 --> 01:48:02.226 line:82%
Let's pay.

1229
01:48:16.157 --> 01:48:19.827 line:82%
Hey, Love Story. Can I buy this for you?

1230
01:48:19.911 --> 01:48:22.580 line:82%
No, thanks. I already have Love Story.

1231
01:48:22.663 --> 01:48:25.166 line:82%
You can only have one love story.

1232
01:48:25.249 --> 01:48:26.709 line:82%
Pooja, come on, let's go.

1233
01:48:28.669 --> 01:48:30.630 line:82%
But I haven't a love story.

1234
01:48:31.172 --> 01:48:33.049 line:82%
I must buy it. This one too.

1235
01:48:33.299 --> 01:48:38.304 line:82%
This better be a nice picture.
Back home in India, I'm a VIP.

1236
01:48:44.560 --> 01:48:47.605 line:82%
The bride's people are always
thrown out of the picture.

1237
01:48:48.147 --> 01:48:50.775 line:82%
How can this family be complete
without me?

1238
01:48:59.659 --> 01:49:03.162 line:82%
Pictures. And nobody told me?

1239
01:49:03.246 --> 01:49:05.832 line:82%
Now you know what we think of you.

1240
01:49:05.915 --> 01:49:09.001 line:82%
At least you think about me.

1241
01:49:13.173 --> 01:49:14.257 line:82%
Excuse me.

1242
01:49:17.177 --> 01:49:18.469 line:82%
What am I doing here?

1243
01:49:20.263 --> 01:49:22.682 line:82%
-Tina, where are you going?
-I'll be right back.

1244
01:49:23.516 --> 01:49:26.644 line:82%
If you won't marry me,
at least take a picture with me.

1245
01:49:26.727 --> 01:49:32.358 line:82%
I can show it around. I'll say I tried
my best, but she wouldn't have me.

1246
01:49:35.736 --> 01:49:39.323 line:82%
-Raj, he's the boy I want for Pooja.
-Okay.

1247
01:49:40.283 --> 01:49:43.369 line:82%
You can convince her. Talk to her.

1248
01:49:46.289 --> 01:49:51.627 line:82%
They look good together, don't they?
l think Pooja will agree to marry Rohan.

1249
01:49:51.711 --> 01:49:53.671 line:82%
What do you think?

1250
01:49:54.505 --> 01:49:56.632 line:82%
I'm waiting for her to agree too.

1251
01:49:58.342 --> 01:50:00.011 line:82%
I'm waiting for her to say yes.

1252
01:50:17.903 --> 01:50:19.655 line:82%
You wanted to see me?

1253
01:50:19.739 --> 01:50:21.157 line:82%
Hi, Pooja.

1254
01:50:22.533 --> 01:50:23.569 line:82%
Chips?

1255
01:50:27.872 --> 01:50:30.583 line:82%
Pooja, I have to talk to you
about something important.

1256
01:50:31.876 --> 01:50:34.086 line:82%
Your mom gave me a big responsibility.

1257
01:50:36.255 --> 01:50:37.840 line:82%
She approves of Rohan.

1258
01:50:39.633 --> 01:50:43.387 line:82%
She thinks I'm the only one
who can talk to you about him,

1259
01:50:46.098 --> 01:50:50.019 line:82%
that I'm the only one who can
convince you to marry him.

1260
01:50:53.230 --> 01:50:54.523 line:82%
What do you think?

1261
01:50:56.525 --> 01:50:57.565 line:82%
Stop it.

1262
01:50:59.695 --> 01:51:03.324 line:82%
I'm not joking, Pooja.
l have to give your mother an answer.

1263
01:51:05.493 --> 01:51:06.952 line:82%
What should I tell her?

1264
01:51:08.829 --> 01:51:11.957 line:82%
l can't say yes to marrying someone.

1265
01:51:12.041 --> 01:51:16.504 line:82%
Why not? In our country,
arranged marriages are very common.

1266
01:51:17.338 --> 01:51:19.340 line:82%
Our parents' marriages were arranged.

1267
01:51:19.965 --> 01:51:22.009 line:82%
They hadn't even met each other.

1268
01:51:22.093 --> 01:51:27.932 line:82%
You know Rohan and from what I see,
you seem to like him.

1269
01:51:31.435 --> 01:51:33.896 line:82%
Of course, if you're in love
with someone else,

1270
01:51:34.855 --> 01:51:36.315 line:82%
that's different.

1271
01:51:40.569 --> 01:51:42.738 line:82%
Are you in love with someone else?

1272
01:51:45.491 --> 01:51:49.286 line:82%
Tell me, Pooja, are you in love
with someone else?

1273
01:51:50.413 --> 01:51:52.498 line:82%
Stop it, Raj, stop it.

1274
01:51:52.581 --> 01:51:56.669 line:82%
Stop it. That's exactly what
I've been wanting to tell you, Pooja.

1275
01:51:56.752 --> 01:51:59.130 line:82%
Stop it. Stop it now.

1276
01:52:02.049 --> 01:52:04.635 line:82%
Do you enjoy playing
with people's hearts?

1277
01:52:05.594 --> 01:52:09.140 line:82%
First me, then Tina, then Rohan,
and now your parents too.

1278
01:52:11.517 --> 01:52:13.727 line:82%
How many hearts
do you want to break, Pooja?

1279
01:52:15.187 --> 01:52:17.731 line:82%
How many hearts do you want to play with?

1280
01:52:19.066 --> 01:52:21.652 line:82%
What you call play could be real.

1281
01:52:21.735 --> 01:52:24.864 line:82%
Turn this lie into the truth, Pooja,
l dare you.

1282
01:52:25.364 --> 01:52:29.076 line:82%
Agree to marry Rohan, I dare you.

1283
01:52:37.251 --> 01:52:41.255 line:82%
You will never agree to marry, Rohan.

1284
01:52:42.840 --> 01:52:45.676 line:82%
You love me too much, Pooja.

1285
01:52:47.845 --> 01:52:50.347 line:82%
You'll never belong to anyone else.

1286
01:52:53.184 --> 01:52:55.394 line:82%
You love me too much, Pooja.

1287
01:52:58.439 --> 01:53:01.859 line:82%
Enough, Raj. Enough. Stop it now.

1288
01:53:01.942 --> 01:53:07.031 line:82%
Not before you say yes to Rohan.

1289
01:53:09.867 --> 01:53:11.952 line:82%
Then will I hold my silence.

1290
01:53:13.662 --> 01:53:16.582 line:82%
Seven days from now,
Tina and I are getting married.

1291
01:53:17.333 --> 01:53:22.046 line:82%
Listen carefully. Now it's your turn
to make the sacrifice.

1292
01:53:23.547 --> 01:53:26.467 line:82%
If by tomorrow
you haven't said yes to Rohan,

1293
01:53:26.967 --> 01:53:29.803 line:82%
I'll announce in front of everyone
that I love you.

1294
01:53:31.597 --> 01:53:36.393 line:82%
Tomorrow, nobody will be able to stop me.
Tomorrow, don't even try to stop me.

1295
01:53:37.478 --> 01:53:38.854 line:82%
Now you can go.

1296
01:54:08.968 --> 01:54:14.932 line:82%
What desire ravages my heart?

1297
01:54:17.977 --> 01:54:23.816 line:82%
If you ask, I will tell you

1298
01:54:28.862 --> 01:54:33.492 line:82%
Not gold, not diamonds

1299
01:54:33.867 --> 01:54:37.329 line:82%
They are no use to me

1300
01:54:38.497 --> 01:54:43.127 line:82%
Not mansions, not cars

1301
01:54:43.794 --> 01:54:47.172 line:82%
They are no more than showpieces

1302
01:54:48.757 --> 01:54:53.178 line:82%
Give me a heart if you will
Take my heart if you will

1303
01:54:53.637 --> 01:54:57.975 line:82%
Give me a heart if you will
Take my heart if you will

1304
01:54:58.475 --> 01:55:03.082 line:82%
Take, take all I have

1305
01:55:03.147 --> 01:55:06.025 line:82%
But there's no trade in love

1306
01:55:08.694 --> 01:55:12.531 line:82%
Take, take all I have

1307
01:55:13.282 --> 01:55:16.327 line:82%
But there's no trade in love

1308
01:55:17.953 --> 01:55:20.581 line:82%
That's a lie

1309
01:55:22.750 --> 01:55:25.544 line:82%
